    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sandstone composed of clay minerals, especially sedimentary materials such as marl and shale; it emits a peculiar earthy odor when breathed upon.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Arenisca compuesta de minerales arcillosos, en especial materiales sedimentarios tales como margas y pizarras. Exhala un olor a tierra peculiar cuando se quiebra.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
